    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="What are Polls on works?" class="article-title">
          What are Polls on works?
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>Polls are a way to set a survey at the time a work is posted.<br>The poll will display under the caption of the work.<br>You can add whatever question content and answers that you like. However, the question is limited to 140 characters, and answers are limited to 20 characters. Additionally, you can only have 5 answers. Setting a poll is optional, and if you don't add one to your work, no poll will be displayed.<br>The results of the poll will only be displayed to the creator and users who responded.<br><br>▼What works can use Polls?</p>
<table style="width: 722px; height: 302px;">
